axios Instance
-------------------------

-its an independence object that align

usefecthock

first one (<fuction>,<depenpency>)

dependency
to control sideeffect/usefect

1)no depenpency : useefect runs on every render
useEffect(() => {
  //Runs on every render
});
2)empty array as dependency :useefect call happens in the first render
useEffect(() => {
  //Runs only on the first render
}, []);
3)props or states : useEffect call happens in the first Render sa well as every time the value of the props or state change
useEffect(() => {
  //Runs on the first render
  //And any time any dependency value changes
}, [prop, state]);